With its luxuriant greenery, serenity, blissful water bodies & enthralling culture; the magic of Kerala as a holiday destination will never fail to impress. There is something about the stunning palm-fringed stretches of sand at beaches that make it the best escape ever. Kerala is blessed with beach resorts and the most idyllic settings for weekend getaways, staycations & elaborate vacations. Here’s a look at some of them:
